snippet.textDisplay: Conor is a great guy, and it shows in this video. I've met him before. I was out for lunch in Dublin with my grandmother and her friends, he walked in with another guy, and I went up to him to ask for a picture. He was very relaxed and shook my hand. I told him I was a huge fan, and he said he was thankful for the support and would love to meet me again. He was patient when I took the selfie (it was blurry the first time). He gave me a hug and that was that! I'll never forget how respectful he was!
